  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To monitor the frequency of the development of thrombocytopenia in patients with Heparin
      Induced Thrombocytopenia/Heparin Induced Thrombocytopenia and Thrombosis Syndrome receiving
      bivalirudin during Percutaneous Coronary Intervention
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
